            , Cheesemonger, 10r 70l. on the 23d of May last, and gave it to the Prisoners to execute, and they accordingly arrested Pixley, and carried him to Lemon's House in Barnaby-street. Not long after I saw them again, and they told me that they had taken a very good Bail-Bond, sign'd by 
               <persName id="t17250224-56-person299">
